frames.caption: A surreal landscape features a towering mountain with sharp, jagged peaks. In the foreground, stacks of money are piled high, creating a striking contrast between natural and man-made elements.
frames.description: The scene depicts a surreal juxtaposition of a rugged mountain range and an enormous pile of money. The setting is otherworldly, with the mountain's sharp peaks resembling a fantastical or alien landscape.

frames.caption: A towering, jagged mountain peak rises sharply against a clear blue sky, dusted with snow and ice. The foreground is filled with large, angular rocks and a swirling mist, creating a dramatic and dynamic scene. Sunlight highlights the textures of the mountain, emphasizing its ruggedness and grandeur.
frames.description: The scene depicts a majestic mountain landscape with a prominent peak surrounded by rocky terrain and swirling mist. The setting is likely a high-altitude, cold environment, possibly in a remote and untouched natural area.
